Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.26,0:00:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,FOUR YEARS AGO
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.68,0:00:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,PORT OF STIMMER,\NLEIDENSCHAFTLICH
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Diethard Bougainvillea.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.69,0:00:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Your brother is here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.52,0:00:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Gil!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.36,0:00:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How have you been?\NYou look depressed, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.15,0:00:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You look just like Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.45,0:00:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't changed either.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.66,0:00:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Father would not approve\Nof your hair for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.08,0:00:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet he would have cut it off\Nwith a saber.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.33,0:00:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't let him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.58,0:00:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You've always been like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.84,0:00:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.42,0:00:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.68,0:00:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop making that face.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.51,0:01:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought you something nice today\Nto celebrate your promotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.52,0:01:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it? Only use it as a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.94,0:01:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get attached.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.27,0:01:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.45,0:01:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.88,0:01:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I found her in the northeastern war zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.14,0:01:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Her name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.64,0:01:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet Evergarden.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.89,0:01:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She's going to start working today\Nas an Auto Memory Doll apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.98,0:01:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Please train her on everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.02,0:01:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.98,0:01:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't have any facial expressions,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.57,0:01:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,just like a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.49,0:02:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like the dolls...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.74,0:02:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that were named after this industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.75,0:02:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, first off...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.04,0:02:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,How much do you know about\Nwhat Auto Memory Dolls do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.63,0:02:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They write letters\Nat the request of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.05,0:02:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Lt. Colonel Hodgins... I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.55,0:02:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the president told me so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.01,0:02:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.10,0:02:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say that I completely understand,\Nbut I think I can perform my duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.73,0:02:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that easy! "Duties?!"\NWhat are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Iris, that's enough. Get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.57,0:02:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.32,0:02:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That reminds me, I haven't introduced\Nthe other Dolls to you yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.58,0:02:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"Doll" refers to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.83,0:02:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand it's an abbreviation\Nfor Auto Memory Doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.08,0:02:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-I figured it out the other day.\N-That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.79,0:02:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl just now... Her name is Iris.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.42,0:02:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a new hire who just\Ncompleted her training course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.63,0:02:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's Erica.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.72,0:03:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She and I have both been working\Nas Dolls for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.34,0:03:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This company is still pretty young,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.18,0:03:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,so, we're all like rookies here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.31,0:03:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.60,0:03:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet, do you know\Nhow to use a typewriter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.86,0:03:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never used one before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.98,0:03:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why don't you start off\Nby practicing typing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.99,0:03:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that easy to become a Doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.28,0:03:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Iris, can we borrow your manual?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.74,0:03:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.58,0:03:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.88,0:03:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.55,0:03:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You should remove your gloves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.55,0:03:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.56,0:03:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.98,0:03:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.81,0:04:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why don't you try it out a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.61,0:04:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Set the paper like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.07,0:04:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn the knob and feed it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.41,0:04:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Place your pointer fingers on the\NF and J keys, and try typing something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.58,0:04:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.29,0:04:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.17,0:04:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Just memorize where your fingers\Nshould go for the different letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.09,0:04:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Try typing what it says in this manual.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait. Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.09,0:05:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you type a little more...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.39,0:05:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,quietly?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.61,0:05:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.32,0:05:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 1.2 Liber. So, that's 10 Corse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.41,0:05:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-Thank you.\N-It's finally time for lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.53,0:05:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Nerine, Lilian.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.99,0:05:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have lunch together.\NI've bought fried noodles for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.62,0:05:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't come to the reception\Nlooking so sweaty like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.64,0:05:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,When you see a man\Nwho's been toiling away,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.39,0:05:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,can't you at least say,\N"Thanks for your hard work"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.48,0:05:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And what do they mean, "Don't come"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.56,0:06:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-Women these days are so calculating.\N-And their perfume stinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.73,0:06:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just trying to\Nsnag rich guys at reception.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.90,0:06:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.95,0:06:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares. No more working girls for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hey, you guys. Fried noodles.\N-I don't want any.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And stop calling me "Hey, you."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have some fried noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.92,0:06:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm stuck just writing\Naddresses again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.63,0:06:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The two reservations\Nwe have this afternoon
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.97,0:06:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,both asked for Cattleya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.68,0:06:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.89,0:06:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.64,0:06:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I came all the way to Leiden\Nto become a Doll,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.73,0:06:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,but all I do is write addresses
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.52,0:06:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and inquiries about missing people\Nfrom the war every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.49,0:06:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.28,0:06:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, I heard that new girl\Nused to be in the army.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though she's still a child?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And....
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.96,0:07:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't have to make her a Doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She's cold and inconsiderate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.13,0:07:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not right for this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.84,0:07:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to write letters\Nthat are more exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.72,0:07:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a letter for a famous person.\NOr a secret love letter for an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.89,0:07:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But those jobs always go to Cattleya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.52,0:07:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Violet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.15,0:07:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I invited her to lunch,\Nbut she said she didn't need to recharge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.28,0:07:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She's just been practicing typing\Nthe entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.78,0:07:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.70,0:07:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for all the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.41,0:07:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, then treat me to dinner, Claudia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.33,0:07:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call me by my first name!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.08,0:07:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because you wanted a girl.\NI can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.05,0:07:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Calling out a girl's name in bed.\NThat was terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.97,0:07:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Please! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.35,0:07:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take you anytime soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.64,0:08:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not getting paid this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.16,0:08:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done writing the addresses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.58,0:08:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.79,0:08:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring these\Nto the delivery department.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.16,0:08:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.71,0:08:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet, thanks for your hard work.\NThat's enough for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.05,0:08:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You've improved a lot! Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This weapon is what's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.26,0:08:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Weapon. You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.72,0:08:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a weapon for working girls like us\Nto go out into society and fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.23,0:08:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have you sit next to a real Doll\Ntomorrow and shadow her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.73,0:08:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going out for a delivery service now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.82,0:08:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone requests it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.15,0:08:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,we go to their house\Nor workplace to write for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.28,0:08:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I take this with me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.24,0:09:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The typewriter? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.66,0:09:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,To my room. For training,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.12,0:09:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and for...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.85,0:09:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Address? Gilbert's?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I want to tell him that I've started\Na writing job and begun training.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.35,0:09:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to report my current status.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.48,0:09:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the major is still busy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.98,0:09:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and can't see me yet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.82,0:09:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.28,0:09:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I'll send this for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.25,0:09:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How's training going?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.34,0:09:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Like you already know,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.13,0:09:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,it's hard making ends meet every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.67,0:09:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,"As you already know,\Nliving expenses are tight."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.43,0:10:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.05,0:10:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him I'll pay back\Ntwo chlor every month.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,-"Every month."\N-If you pay back two chlor every month,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.85,0:10:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,it will take you 120 years\Nto pay back everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, will you be able to\Nsurvive until then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.36,0:10:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, she's really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.78,0:10:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But sometimes she gets really mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.95,0:10:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm sorry for hurting\Nyour precious child."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.54,0:10:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I didn't discipline her well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.04,0:10:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"Our teachings were insufficient."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.13,0:10:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.75,0:10:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I do wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.25,0:10:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-Um...\N-Crying gets in the way of our work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.34,0:10:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-Please stop crying immediately.\N-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.43,0:10:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What do you mean by this letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.93,0:10:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm sorry for my selfish request..."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.52,0:10:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-What do you mean, "selfish?"\N-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.94,0:10:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,"I apologize for the delay?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.32,0:10:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This makes it seem like it's all my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:10:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think you are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.11,0:11:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She's Erica.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't ask her name!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.57,0:11:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, I don't like this letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not paying for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.45,0:11:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Refusing to pay because\Nyou didn't like it is illegal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.00,0:11:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What don't you like about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be specific.\NPlease give us some guidance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.63,0:11:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And provide brief input.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.55,0:11:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We've received complaints\Nfrom a few customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.72,0:11:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Was there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.52,0:11:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.64,0:11:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.85,0:11:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,-There is nothing wrong with my health.\N-No, I mean about working as a Doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm training diligently.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.78,0:11:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.20,0:11:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... We don't have\Nany more reservations today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.66,0:11:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to work diligently together
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.12,0:11:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to make the membership list for the\NChamber of Commerce after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.33,0:11:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Type the company and the address.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.34,0:11:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-And the type of industry.\N-Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.26,0:12:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Why do you want to do this job?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.39,0:12:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.77,0:12:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is everyone gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.52,0:12:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome. Do you want to request a letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,-Why else would I be here?\N-My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.91,0:12:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If you request it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.95,0:12:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll write any type of document for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.04,0:12:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Auto Memory Doll Service.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the Doll\Nnamed Cattleya Baudelaire?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.46,0:12:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,She's on a business trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.42,0:12:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I came here because I heard\Nyou can never go wrong with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.47,0:12:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone asked me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.34,0:12:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A man who started an automobile company.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.10,0:12:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He said every household\Nis going to own a car in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.18,0:12:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.48,0:12:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But, you know...\NI'm not such a simple woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.23,0:12:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want him to think I'm easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.61,0:13:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, in other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.74,0:13:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he's not that great of a catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.45,0:13:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any feelings for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.95,0:13:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If he showed me he's serious,\Nand if he really loves me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.25,0:13:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Please write an elegant\Nand romantic letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.21,0:13:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.50,0:13:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.22,0:13:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Are you the one\Nwho's going to write it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.22,0:13:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.66,0:13:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with that letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.45,0:13:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am, please calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.49,0:13:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Iris. Bring some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.41,0:13:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.41,0:13:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,-I wrote it just as you requested.\N-What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.25,0:14:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He got angry and sent\Nthe letter back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.63,0:14:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Read it! Read what you wrote!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.22,0:14:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"I read your letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.30,0:14:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I do not have feelings\Nfor you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.26,0:14:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, your seriousness\Nand love are insufficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a complex and serious woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.52,0:14:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Please reconsider again
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.52,0:14:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,with gifts and funds."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.03,0:14:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with this letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.66,0:14:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.45,0:14:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The expressions used were too straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.83,0:14:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.29,0:14:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,wanted to date him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.29,0:14:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I accepted his request too soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.67,0:14:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,he would think that I'm too easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.92,0:14:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Women want men to chase them,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.05,0:14:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.80,0:14:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I... loved him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.11,0:15:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.19,0:15:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Water or hot water\Nis enough for rehydrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Two cups of flower tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.20,0:15:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.87,0:15:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It might have been too soon\Nto give you such a hard job.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.71,0:15:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm incapable of understanding.\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I wrote the letter incorporating\Nher requests as much as I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.55,0:15:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Words can have different interpretations.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.01,0:15:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What one says isn't the whole truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a human weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.73,0:15:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They test others to confirm\Ntheir own existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.40,0:15:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a contradiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.61,0:15:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to apologize to him in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.13,0:16:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.43,0:16:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Major!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.52,0:16:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Major Gilbert!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.65,0:16:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.49,0:16:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.83,0:16:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Are you alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.45,0:16:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You look sad. Are you eating well?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.87,0:16:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I've replenished my nutrients.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.54,0:16:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then did you make a mistake at work?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.88,0:16:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back to the delivery department.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.47,0:17:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing deliveries is no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.35,0:17:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about working as a Doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.23,0:17:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it better to find another job?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.23,0:17:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I should look for a job, too.\NHodgins said
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.11,0:17:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,he's not getting paid this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.53,0:17:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like our company isn't doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.85,0:17:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I suited to become an Auto Memory Doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.94,0:17:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I was also...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.94,0:17:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not asking about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.49,0:18:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not suited for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.37,0:18:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you want to do this job\Nin the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.13,0:18:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know what "I love you" means.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.51,0:18:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.47,0:18:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.97,0:18:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that those words\Nexpress a particular emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.85,0:18:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did the major say\Nthose words to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.94,0:18:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.44,0:18:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I still want to continue with this job,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.07,0:18:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,even if I'm not suited for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.96,0:18:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a towel in the locker room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.88,0:18:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.92,0:18:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I think working as a Doll\Nis too hard for Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.01,0:19:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This company is still new,\Nbut we get so many requests for Cattleya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.80,0:19:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we get a bad reputation\Nbecause of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Just when things are about to take off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.23,0:19:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's better to have Violet quit.\N-No, give her a little more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.36,0:19:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.19,0:19:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Erica!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.03,0:19:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And Violet, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.03,0:19:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.03,0:19:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.53,0:19:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think we should make her quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.04,0:19:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She... Violet...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.33,0:19:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,is very accurate and fast when she types,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.71,0:19:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and she can do tasks like making\Nmembership lists and writing addresses.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.59,0:19:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Once she learns more...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.05,0:19:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she'll be able to write letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.43,0:19:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.43,0:19:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make her quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.39,0:19:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a contradiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.69,0:19:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You said I'm not suited for this duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.61,0:19:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a contradiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.45,0:20:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who isn't suited\Nto being an Auto Memory Doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.54,0:20:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I got so serious\Nabout defending her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.13,0:20:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The machine that was a prototype\Nfor the typewriter
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.22,0:20:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,was originally invented by Dr. Orland,\Nthe authority on letterpress printing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,His wife, Mollie, was a novelist,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.85,0:20:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,but she became blind\Nand couldn't write anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.19,0:20:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He created the typewriter for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.32,0:20:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The doctor called it the Auto Memory Doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.74,0:20:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That term now refers to the\Nindustry of writing for others.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.74,0:20:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Meeting her made me remember\Nmy dream, which I had almost forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.75,0:20:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,My feelings, which were buried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.50,0:21:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like how my heart was moved\Nby the novels written by Orland's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.63,0:21:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm going to close up shop. Are you okay?\N-Uh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.77,0:21:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.23,0:21:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to write beautiful letters\Nthat can move peoples' hearts, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.37,0:21:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.87,0:21:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.46,0:21:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice. Violet, stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.83,0:21:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.59,0:21:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks good on you.\NI was right after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.89,0:21:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and don't forget this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.56,0:21:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for being late.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.15,0:22:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.44,0:22:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.32,0:22:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it.\NThis is the brooch the major gave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.33,0:22:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It was on the black market.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.49,0:22:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone must have stolen it\Nfrom your belongings.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.80,0:22:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah! Violet,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.22,0:22:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,do you want to attend\Na Doll training course?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.97,0:22:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They have short-term courses, too.\NIris attended one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.22,0:22:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The teacher is really strict.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.14,0:22:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it'll be good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.73,0:22:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You bought that back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.48,0:22:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you didn't get paid this month?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.40,0:22:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.74,0:22:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, who is the major she talks about?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.79,0:23:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Gilbert.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.09,0:23:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a friend\Nfrom my Military Academy days.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.21,0:23:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He's from the Bougainvillea family.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.26,0:23:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! That margrave...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.93,0:23:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Even though he's from a rich family,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.65,0:23:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,he was a man with spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.94,0:23:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,"Was"?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.38,0:23:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.76,0:23:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,NOT COMING BACK
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.92,0:23:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,coming back anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.01,0:23:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Subtitle translation by\NHoday Stearns
